snippet.title: Skyhook Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Skyhook is out now on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/361350/

Fight with grappling hooks in this party platformer anbd play as a shark riding a gryphon!

For more information, visit http://skyhookgame.com

Follow me on Twitter and Facebook:
http://twitter.com/qazitv
http://facebook.com/SkyhookGame

Game by Wase Qazi - http://twitch.tv/qazitv
Music by Julian Shanahan - https://www.youtube.com/julianshanaha...
Illustrations by Katherine Murray - http://www.kmurrayart.com/
